  <title translate="true">Observation Process</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">observation</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Observation Process</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The Observation process is used to compare model-generated values of head, flux, or advective transport with observed values. &#160;During model calibration, the goal is to reduce the discrepencies between the two. &#160;Many of the input files for the observation process are linked to specific input files for the Groundwater Flow process.</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="IF" value="ALLMODELS,MODFLOW-2000"/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="OBS" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Input File For All Observations</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Input File For All Observations </text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(required in MODFLOW-2000, not included in MODFLOW-2005 or MODFLOW-LGR)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="HOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Head-Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="CHOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Constant-Head Flow Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="DROB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Drain Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="IF" value="ALLMODELS,MODFLOW-2000"/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="DTOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Drain Return Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Drain Return Observation </text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">package (optional, only included in MODFLOW-2000)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="RVOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">River Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="GBOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">General-Head-Boundary Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="IF" value="ALLMODELS,MODFLOW-2000,MODFLOW-2005,MODFLOW-CFP,MODFLOW-LGR,MODFLOW-NWT"/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="STOB" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Stream Observation</link><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Stream Observation</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> package (optional, not included in MODFLOW-OWHM)</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="IF" value="ALLMODELS,MODFLOW-2000"/><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="ADV2" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Advective-Transport Observation</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">&#32;</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Advective-Transport Observation package </text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(optional, only included in MODFLOW-2000)</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><conditional-text type="IF" value="ALLMODELS,MODFLOW-NWT"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">In MODFLOW-NWT, if the head solution from one simulation will be used as </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="BAS6" anchor="STRT" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">starting heads</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> for a subsequent simulation, or if the Observation Process is used (Harbaugh and others, 2000), then </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="UPW_Upstream_Weighting_Package" anchor="HDRY" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">HDRY</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> should not be printed to the output file for dry cells (that is, the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="UPW_Upstream_Weighting_Package" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">UPW</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> Package input variable should be set as </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="UPW_Upstream_Weighting_Package" anchor="IPHDRY" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">IPHDRY</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">=0).</text><conditional-text type="END"/></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
